User - Class in com.kugelschlag.SpringPwdValidator.models
A super simple user data object just to drive testing of password validation The "@CharterPWValid" tag is a custom annotation that checks for certain string inputs - configurable The "@NotNull" is part of the standard valdation package
User() - Constructor for class com.kugelschlag.SpringPwdValidator.models.User
 
User(String, String) - Constructor for class com.kugelschlag.SpringPwdValidator.models.User
 
UserController - Class in com.kugelschlag.SpringPwdValidator.controllers
UserController is just a very simple REST controller used to access testing of a custom password validator It maps the URI to Post a User object that has been tagged for validation On validation success, it will return a 200 code and a ResponseEntity with the User object On validation failure, it will return a 400 code with a string array of messages describing the validation errors
